metadata.name: Nucleid City Storm #1
metadata.description:
I captured the most amazing North Sea cloud formations rolling into the city of Ostend, Belgium from over seas on a late sunday afternoon. Like waves hitting both from below and above. This particular storm made for some very interesting contrasts.

1/1 - Minted Feb 2022 by Andy Decramer (@NucleusPhoto) on Foundation.app as part of the "Nucleid City Storm" Collection.
